- Shut up and fish!</i>

05:49.782 --> 05:51.977
No. I got nothing to say to you.

05:52.051 --> 05:54.315
- Nothing personal.
- Thank you.

05:54.887 --> 05:56.320
<i>Nice yard! It's nice!</i>

05:56.389 --> 05:57.947
How's that restraining order coming?

05:58.024 --> 06:00.720
