like this thing you're doing with my butt.

06:05.164 --> 06:07.894
What are you doing here? Stop doing it!

06:08.434 --> 06:10.732
Wait, no. No, wait. Keep doing it.

06:10.803 --> 06:12.532
Let me go get my camera!

06:12.605 --> 06:15.335
